        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You shout or make a loud noise, projecting your voice towards your target. Your magic creates a terrible illusion to accompany your frightening sound, attempting to startle your target and disrupt their focus.</em></p><div><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[frightened]. While they are frightened in this way, they have disadvantage on &amp;reference[concentration] saves.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul></div><p></p><div><div><p><strong>Upcasting</strong>: Target one additional creature for each spell level above 1st.</p></div></div>",
